name: Tic-Tac-Toe 2013
overview: Tic-Tac-Toe 2013 is a public domain/freeware computerized version of the popular centuries old pen-and-paper game of the same name. This version was developed by Juga64 in 2013. it can be played as both a single player game against the computer, or as a two player game with a second player.
